review: Appointment went really well. Doctor was friendly, professional, and explained everything in detail with patience.

Please don't visit with this doctor. My baby boy detected beta thalassemia. Which is so major and critical disease. She not suggest or checked the test when my wife pregnant.God promise  I am really so depressed. Please avoid this doctor. **** **** ** ****** ** ******* ** ******** Please my request don't counsell with this doctor ***** * ** ********* *****

tags: Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,
review: we have been visiting this Doctor from last 1year, we are not aware wats going on. recently we have visited this Doctor for early pregnancy and she said it's ectopic pregnancy, and ask for couple of scanning reports day1 and day 3,and she confirmed this is ectopic pregnancy which needs to remove on the same day with out delay, and that needs to remove through surgery. we ware upset and just to confirm we went for second opinion in different hospital, This Doctor also ask for all the scanning reports and did the check up for around 30mins *** ********* **** ** ****** *** ******* ********** ** **** ******* *** ********* ********** ***** *** ******** ******** ***** *** *** ** ** **** ***** * *****  *** ** ******* ****** ***** ****** *** *******  ***** *** ********* ** **** ** ***** **** ******* ********** it's been 2months now and baby heartbeat also started.. we are happy.this is the very bad experience I had with this doctor, ** ******* *** **** ******** ****** ****** ** *** ****** ********
Kind and made me feel comfortable.  Explained everything in detail. Cleared all my doubts whenever needed.

We went for pregnancy test, doctor is asking some silly questions and she is not encouraging pregnancy with in 1 or 2 years of marriage. *** ** ******* *** ******* ** **** ****** ** *** ******* Even if we tell about our symptoms she is getting more anger. Bad place to vist. ****** **** **** **** *** **** **** ****** **** *** **** *** ***** *** *****  *** **** ***** **** ******** ****** *** **** **** ** ** **** **** Not recommended
